  <li>
    <p>Thus it had <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="fallen to him - (to do something)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(落到了他的肩膀上)</code></b> to add up the number of deaths during the last few days, and, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="being of an obliging disposition"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(有那么一点)</code></b>, he had volunteered to bring a copy of the latest figures to the doctor.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Rieux had already noticed Grand’s <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="trick of - (doing something)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(有...的特别的/特有的习惯)</code></b> <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="professing"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(乐于做某事)</code></b> to quote some <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title=""><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(这里是措辞的意思)</code></b> of speech from “his part of the world” (he hailed from Montélimar), and following up with some such hackneyed expression as “lost in dreams,” or “pretty as a picture.”</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Grand put a hand up to his hat and <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="tugged it down"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(将它拉下来)</code></b> upon his big, protruding ears, then murmured some half-inaudible remark from which Rieux seemed to gather that Grand’s work was connected with “the growth of a personality.”</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Though he still had most of the teeth in his lower jaw, all the upper ones were gone, with the result that when he smiled, raising his upper lip—the lower scarcely moved—his mouth looked like <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="a small black hole let into his face"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(一个通向他的脸部的小黑洞)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>They started off toward the Place d’Armes. Cottard still kept silent. <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="The streets were beginning to fill up"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(街上人开始多起来了)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>“Well,” he said, “perhaps we’d better make up our minds to <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="call this disease by its name"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(弄清除这种病的名字)</code></b>. So far we’ve been only <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="shillyshallying"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(犹豫不决/优柔寡断)</code></b>. Look here, I’m off to the laboratory; like to come with me?”</p>
  </li>
</ol>
